{"tid":2304870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施政報告評分創史上新低　林鄭形容「平穩落地」　自誇「建設性高」","createTime":"2020-11-29T07:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T04:19:28.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f4f9fc612d8abb517ec402278aae380b4e3d4c4e","tid":2304870,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:20:50.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n林鄭今天於無綫節目《講清講楚》指，由國教爭議、佔領行動到《逃犯條例》風波，追本溯源都離不開外界對一國兩制的理解、是否準確把握中央及香港關係等；被問到將香港的深層次問題一次過「擺上枱面」，對香港的破壞性是否歷來最高時，林鄭稱：「反轉嚟講，就係我嘅建設性亦高啲啦」，指若相關深層次問題值得處理，不應迴避。至於任內對香港的建設是否多於破壞時，她稱：「我一定係基於呢個信念，我先繼續坐喺度做行政長官，如果我每一日做行長官，係破壞緊我一個咁深愛嘅地方，我唔會再坐喺度」。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201129/AKJ6N2YJNRG35HIYDAAAQIZKUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201129%2FAKJ6N2YJNRG35HIYDAAAQIZKUE%2F&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=74625276\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201129%2FAKJ6N2YJNRG35HIYDAAAQIZKUE%2F&h=ee5742ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201129/AKJ6N2YJNRG35HIYDAAAQIZKUE/</a>"},{"pid":"18d72413acac199de648555bf3148f9a05cf7dff","tid":2304870,"uid":55011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:23:04.000Z","msg":"點樣反轉嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95592432ce73507eec3cba32fa41ac1e43022078","tid":2304870,"uid":204227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:23:11.000Z","msg":"以為心軟論已經夠荒謬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e15297c300caed32a0573a6b8f3dac84374c5a","tid":2304870,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:23:30.000Z","msg":"夠講過辭職啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b3c65ade23f520c0b2d2d71c332625817f279a","tid":2304870,"uid":69746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T0